datatype mynat = MyZero ("0") | MySuc mynat

fun myadd :: "mynat \<Rightarrow> mynat \<Rightarrow> mynat" where

fun mymul :: "mynat \<Rightarrow> mynat \<Rightarrow> mynat" where
  "mymul MyZero m = MyZero" |
  "mymul (MySuc n) m = myadd m (mymul n m)"
